Electricity supply will be interrupted in the i&#8217;Langa area on the 26th of March 2017 between 14:00 and 18:00.The outages is scheduled to allow the City of Mbombela to do maintenance on the i&#8217;Langa switching stations and i&#8217;Langa Mall contractors to move the main supply cables at i&#8217;Langa Mall to the new entrance.Please note that all installations must be regarded as live and that the date and time might be postponed until further notice due to bad weather.